        <div class="d-flex  align-items-stretch">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <div class="content shadow-sm br-10 p-4 h-100 bl-bg">
                    <p>The collection of problems in physics edited by O.Y. Savchenko has remained one of the most
                        sought-after resources for physics olympiad preparation in post-soviet countries for over 30
                        years. However, during this time, not a single complete solution manual for this collection has
                        been created.</p>
                    <p>This website presents a non-profit project aimed at collaboratively creating the first solution
                        manual with solutions from different authors. Currently, more than 745 solutions out of 2023
                        problems have been published. The project, launched in 2023, is actively developing in both
                        Russian and English. If you would like to join the work, read how-to-contribute guide.</p>
